{
  "video_id": "zawpbVpu5nY",
  "title": "Why people of different faiths are painting their houses of worship yellow | Nabila Alibhai",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12580.0,
      "end_time": 14580.0,
      "text": "We live in a time of fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15620.0,
      "end_time": 18996.0,
      "text": "and our response to fear can either be to contract"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19200.0,
      "end_time": 20820.0,
      "text": "and attempt to guard ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21820.0,
      "end_time": 24956.0,
      "text": "or to extend ourselves, hold on to each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24980.0,
      "end_time": 26740.0,
      "text": "and face our fears together."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27980.0,
      "end_time": 29420.0,
      "text": "What is your instinct?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30500.0,
      "end_time": 32420.0,
      "text": "What do you see more of in the world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34600.0,
      "end_time": 36360.0,
      "text": "The problem with the first approach"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36600.0,
      "end_time": 38396.0,
      "text": "is that in our mounting isolation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38420.0,
      "end_time": 41360.0,
      "text": "we divide ourselves from others."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41600.0,
      "end_time": 43476.0,
      "text": "Our sense of isolation grows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43500.0,
      "end_time": 45636.0,
      "text": "because our imagination goes into overdrive"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45660.0,
      "end_time": 49196.0,
      "text": "about the people and the spaces that we no longer engage with."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49220.0,
      "end_time": 52660.0,
      "text": "Our sense of otherness grows, and we lose empathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54380.0,
      "end_time": 56796.0,
      "text": "Today I&#39;m going to tell you about a group of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56820.0,
      "end_time": 58956.0,
      "text": "that took the global challenge of terrorism"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58980.0,
      "end_time": 63660.0,
      "text": "and began creating spaces where strangers connect in solidarity."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64739.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68580.0,
      "text": "My own obsession with what I see as irrational divisions began as a child."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69660.0,
      "end_time": 73836.0,
      "text": "As a fourth-generation Kenyan Muslim of Indian origin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 73860.0,
      "end_time": 75795.0,
      "text": "it bothered me that in four generations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 75820.0,
      "end_time": 77875.0,
      "text": "there wasn&#39;t a single marriage in my family"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77900.0,
      "end_time": 80200.0,
      "text": "outside of my small religious community."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 80700.0,
      "end_time": 82380.0,
      "text": "And I wondered what that was about."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 83420.0,
      "end_time": 85196.0,
      "text": "Was it fear?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85220.0,
      "end_time": 86539.0,
      "text": "Was it racism?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 88600.0,
      "end_time": 89620.0,
      "text": "Was it cultural preservation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90580.0,
      "end_time": 92676.0,
      "text": "Did it have something to do with colonialism?"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 94600.0,
      "end_time": 97940.0,
      "text": "Certainly, we didn&#39;t share a lot of the same public spaces with others."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 99500.0,
      "end_time": 103600.0,
      "text": "These divisions bothered me deeply, and they drove my career choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 104220.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "When I was 20, the US embassies in Kenya and Tanzania were bombed."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 110900.0,
      "end_time": 113156.0,
      "text": "A year later, I was on my way to the Middle East"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 113180.0,
      "end_time": 114660.0,
      "text": "to study conflict resolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 115700.0,
      "end_time": 117760.0,
      "text": "And then from that point on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 117100.0,
      "end_time": 120636.0,
      "text": "it wasn&#39;t very hard for me to find insecure environments to work in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 120660.0,
      "end_time": 122515.0,
      "text": "because the world was quickly shifting"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 122540.0,
      "end_time": 124860.0,
      "text": "in what we now know as the time of terrorism."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 125740.0,
      "end_time": 128995.0,
      "text": "I was in Washington, DC when 9/11 happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 129199.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132476.0,
      "text": "and then I moved back home to Kenya to work with refugees"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 132500.0,
      "end_time": 134636.0,
      "text": "and then later worked in Pakistan"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 134660.0,
      "end_time": 136140.0,
      "text": "and in Afghanistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 137940.0,
      "end_time": 140596.0,
      "text": "In all of these places, what I noticed"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 140620.0,
      "end_time": 143156.0,
      "text": "was how important physical spaces are"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 143180.0,
      "end_time": 145556.0,
      "text": "to making us feel safe"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 145580.0,
      "end_time": 146876.0,
      "text": "and well"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 146900.0,
      "end_time": 148100.0,
      "text": "and like we belong."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 149580.0,
      "end_time": 153100.0,
      "text": "In 2013, I came back home to Nairobi from Afghanistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 154460.0,
      "end_time": 157596.0,
      "text": "Al-Shabaab operatives had besieged Westgate shopping center,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 157620.0,
      "end_time": 161620.0,
      "text": "killing 67 people in a day of utter horror."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 163860.0,
      "end_time": 165756.0,
      "text": "Soon after that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 165780.0,
      "end_time": 168236.0,
      "text": "I could see how Nairobi was beginning to change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 173196.0,
      "text": "and it was beginning to feel more like the fear and terror-weary"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 173220.0,
      "end_time": 175740.0,
      "text": "and war-torn cities that I had worked in."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 177600.0,
      "end_time": 180380.0,
      "text": "And Nairobi continues to grow in fear-driven ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 181140.0,
      "end_time": 183676.0,
      "text": "We see more walls, more barriers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 183700.0,
      "end_time": 184940.0,
      "text": "more security."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 185820.0,
      "end_time": 187476.0,
      "text": "And like other parts of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 187500.0,
      "end_time": 191660.0,
      "text": "we are experiencing an erosion of human connection."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 192140.0,
      "end_time": 195236.0,
      "text": "Divisions along religious lines are deepening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 195260.0,
      "end_time": 198780.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re doubting more and more how much we have in common."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 200420.0,
      "end_time": 201715.0,
      "text": "We are at a pivotal time"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 201740.0,
      "end_time": 205276.0,
      "text": "when we need to restore our confidence in humanity"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 205300.0,
      "end_time": 208180.0,
      "text": "and stand boldly and visibly together."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 209700.0,
      "end_time": 212476.0,
      "text": "So in 2014, I brought together a group of people in Nairobi"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 212500.0,
      "end_time": 213740.0,
      "text": "to figure out what to do:"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 214500.0,
      "end_time": 219460.0,
      "text": "public intellectuals, diplomats, artists, development workers."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 220340.0,
      "end_time": 223620.0,
      "text": "And the group articulated our challenge as threefold:"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 224820.0,
      "end_time": 228756.0,
      "text": "one, to reclaim the city from the narrative of terrorism"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 228780.0,
      "end_time": 231996.0,
      "text": "and back into the hands of the people that live there;"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 232200.0,
      "end_time": 236760.0,
      "text": "two, introduce a language beyond race, tribe or religion"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 236100.0,
      "end_time": 239476.0,
      "text": "that would help us transcend our differences;"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 239500.0,
      "end_time": 244360.0,
      "text": "and three, provide a gesture that would help restore empathy"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 244600.0,
      "end_time": 246420.0,
      "text": "and conversation and trust."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 248340.0,
      "end_time": 251316.0,
      "text": "One of the people in this group was an artist and architect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 251340.0,
      "end_time": 253200.0,
      "text": "Yazmany Arboleda."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 253860.0,
      "end_time": 256636.0,
      "text": "He and I have collaborated in other parts of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 256660.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258236.00000000003,
      "text": "over many years."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 258260.0,
      "end_time": 259796.0,
      "text": "He has a history"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 259820.0,
      "end_time": 262356.0,
      "text": "of disrupting urban environments"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 262380.0,
      "end_time": 264360.0,
      "text": "and making strangers connect"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 264600.0,
      "end_time": 267220.0,
      "text": "in incredible, beautiful and spectacular ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 268700.0,
      "end_time": 270436.0,
      "text": "He had an idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 270460.0,
      "end_time": 273596.0,
      "text": "The idea was to unite people of different faiths"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 273620.0,
      "end_time": 276796.0,
      "text": "by getting them to paint each other&#39;s houses of worship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 276820.0,
      "end_time": 280516.0,
      "text": "mosques, temples, synagogues, churches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 280540.0,
      "end_time": 282476.0,
      "text": "paint them yellow"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 282500.0,
      "end_time": 283860.0,
      "text": "in the name of love."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 285980.0,
      "end_time": 289316.0,
      "text": "By focusing on icons of faith,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 289340.0,
      "end_time": 293395.0,
      "text": "we would get people to reexamine the true essence of their faith,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 293420.0,
      "end_time": 297300.0,
      "text": "the common belief that we share in kindness, generosity and friendship."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 298620.0,
      "end_time": 301636.0,
      "text": "By creating pathways between houses of worship"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 301660.0,
      "end_time": 303276.0,
      "text": "within one neighborhood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 303300.0,
      "end_time": 305196.0,
      "text": "we would create islands of stability"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 305220.0,
      "end_time": 306636.0,
      "text": "and networks of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 306660.0,
      "end_time": 309180.0,
      "text": "that could withstand threats."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 309980.0,
      "end_time": 313500.0,
      "text": "And neighbors, by picking up a paintbrush with other neighbors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 314540.0,
      "end_time": 316556.0,
      "text": "would engage not just with their heads"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 316580.0,
      "end_time": 318900.0,
      "text": "but with their hands and with their hearts."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 320140.0,
      "end_time": 323276.0,
      "text": "And the painted buildings would become sculptures in the landscape"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 323300.0,
      "end_time": 325956.0,
      "text": "that speak of people from very different backgrounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 325980.0,
      "end_time": 327180.0,
      "text": "that stand together."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 329340.0,
      "end_time": 331340.0,
      "text": "We&#39;d call the project \"Colour in Faith.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 332220.0,
      "end_time": 336276.0,
      "text": "We loved the idea and we immediately began approaching houses of worship:"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 336300.0,
      "end_time": 339760.0,
      "text": "churches, temples, mosques, synagogues."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 339100.0,
      "end_time": 341756.0,
      "text": "Door to door, we went to more than 60 rabbis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 341780.0,
      "end_time": 344299.0,
      "text": "imams, pastors and priests."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 344980.0,
      "end_time": 346436.0,
      "text": "As you can imagine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 346460.0,
      "end_time": 348156.0,
      "text": "bringing these communities together"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 348180.0,
      "end_time": 351396.0,
      "text": "when prejudices are reinforced by a global pandemic of fear"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 351420.0,
      "end_time": 352676.0,
      "text": "is not easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 352700.0,
      "end_time": 353900.0,
      "text": "It was complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 355380.0,
      "end_time": 358360.0,
      "text": "We were confronted with the hierarchy of decision-making"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 358600.0,
      "end_time": 359740.0,
      "text": "within religious establishments."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 360340.0,
      "end_time": 362835.0,
      "text": "For example, with Catholic churches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 362860.0,
      "end_time": 366156.0,
      "text": "we were told that the archbishop would have to make the decision."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 366180.0,
      "end_time": 368276.0,
      "text": "And so we wrote a letter to the archbishop."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 368300.0,
      "end_time": 370100.0,
      "text": "We wrote a letter to the Vatican."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 370660.0,
      "end_time": 372236.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re still waiting to hear back."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 372260.0,
      "end_time": 374116.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 374140.0,
      "end_time": 376195.0,
      "text": "And with other houses of worship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 376220.0,
      "end_time": 379396.0,
      "text": "we were told that the patrons, the people that pay for the building"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 379420.0,
      "end_time": 381956.0,
      "text": "and the construction and the painting of the buildings"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 381980.0,
      "end_time": 383420.0,
      "text": "would have to make a decision."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 384820.0,
      "end_time": 386276.0,
      "text": "And then we came head-to-head"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 386300.0,
      "end_time": 388996.0,
      "text": "with the long legacy of missionary and donor dependence"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 389200.0,
      "end_time": 392316.0,
      "text": "that so impedes unconditional civic action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 392340.0,
      "end_time": 394236.0,
      "text": "and we learned this the hard way."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 394260.0,
      "end_time": 395836.0,
      "text": "There was one community"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 395860.0,
      "end_time": 399196.0,
      "text": "that in our repeated conversations would keep asking us"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 399220.0,
      "end_time": 400820.0,
      "text": "to appreciate them."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 401580.0,
      "end_time": 403596.0,
      "text": "And so we would keep going back"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 403620.0,
      "end_time": 405796.0,
      "text": "and telling them that we appreciate them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 405820.0,
      "end_time": 407635.0,
      "text": "and of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 407660.0,
      "end_time": 410700.0,
      "text": "if we didn&#39;t appreciate them, we wouldn&#39;t be here."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 412900.0,
      "end_time": 415395.0,
      "text": "And then we learned painfully late in the game"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 415420.0,
      "end_time": 419980.0,
      "text": "that the word \"appreciation\" is code for getting paid to participate."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 421300.0,
      "end_time": 423260.0,
      "text": "And so we challenged them"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 424420.0,
      "end_time": 426236.0,
      "text": "and we asked the question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 426260.0,
      "end_time": 427500.0,
      "text": "\"So what will it cost?"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 428460.0,
      "end_time": 430600.0,
      "text": "How much could we pay you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 431580.0,
      "end_time": 434300.0,
      "text": "And if we pay for your faith, is it really faith?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 435660.0,
      "end_time": 438276.0,
      "text": "We started the project asking the question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 438300.0,
      "end_time": 440476.0,
      "text": "\"Where does your faith live?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 440500.0,
      "end_time": 442756.0,
      "text": "And here we found ourselves asking the question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 442780.0,
      "end_time": 444500.0,
      "text": "\"How much does your faith cost?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 446100.0,
      "end_time": 449980.0,
      "text": "But the most difficult issue was the perceived risk of standing apart."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 450500.0,
      "end_time": 454396.0,
      "text": "We had one synagogue that flat-out refused to participate"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 454420.0,
      "end_time": 456636.0,
      "text": "because it feared drawing attention to itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 456660.0,
      "end_time": 457860.0,
      "text": "and becoming a target."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 458820.0,
      "end_time": 462600.0,
      "text": "Similarly, we had a mosque that also feared becoming a target."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 463420.0,
      "end_time": 465300.0,
      "text": "And these fears are justified."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 467300.0,
      "end_time": 472460.0,
      "text": "And yet, there were 25 houses of worship that pledged to participate."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 473180.0,
      "end_time": 478556.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 478580.0,
      "end_time": 483750.0,
      "text": "These bold leaders took the gesture and reinforced it with their own meaning."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 483100.0,
      "end_time": 486600.0,
      "text": "For some, it was to tell the world that they&#39;re not terrorists."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 486740.0,
      "end_time": 490820.0,
      "text": "For others, it was to welcome people through their doors to ask questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 491460.0,
      "end_time": 493316.0,
      "text": "And for some, it was to bridge the gap"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 493340.0,
      "end_time": 495476.0,
      "text": "between the older and the younger generation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 495500.0,
      "end_time": 499996.0,
      "text": "which by the way is something that many faiths are grappling with right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 500200.0,
      "end_time": 503835.0,
      "text": "And for some it was simply to build neighborhood solidarity"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 503860.0,
      "end_time": 506600.0,
      "text": "in advance of feared election violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 507700.0,
      "end_time": 509236.0,
      "text": "When asked why yellow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 509260.0,
      "end_time": 511515.0,
      "text": "one imam beautifully said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 511540.0,
      "end_time": 513460.0,
      "text": "\"Yellow is the color of the sun."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 514220.0,
      "end_time": 516756.0,
      "text": "The sun shines on us all equally."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 516780.0,
      "end_time": 518299.0,
      "text": "It does not discriminate.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 519299.0,
      "end_time": 521996.0,
      "text": "He and others spread the word through their congregations"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 522200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523236.00000000006,
      "text": "and over the radio."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 523260.0,
      "end_time": 525955.0,
      "text": "Municipal government officials stepped forward and helped"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 525979.0,
      "end_time": 530156.0,
      "text": "with permits and with convening civil society organizations."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 530180.0,
      "end_time": 533795.0,
      "text": "A paint company donated a thousand liters of yellow paint"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 533820.0,
      "end_time": 537436.0,
      "text": "mixed especially for us in what they now call \"optimistic yellow.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 537460.0,
      "end_time": 538756.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 538780.0,
      "end_time": 543836.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 543860.0,
      "end_time": 547116.0,
      "text": "And a poetry collective joined forces with a university"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 547140.0,
      "end_time": 549396.0,
      "text": "and hosted a series of tweet chats"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 549420.0,
      "end_time": 551596.0,
      "text": "that challenged the nation on issues of faith,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 551620.0,
      "end_time": 554276.0,
      "text": "our faith not just in the context of religion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 554300.0,
      "end_time": 557996.0,
      "text": "but our faith in politicians and tribe and nation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 558200.0,
      "end_time": 561699.0,
      "text": "our faith in the older generation and in the younger generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 563180.0,
      "end_time": 567360.0,
      "text": "And then Colour in Faith was launched at a gallery event"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 567600.0,
      "end_time": 570555.0,
      "text": "that invited an incredible mix of gallerygoers"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 570580.0,
      "end_time": 574380.0,
      "text": "and religious leaders and artists and businesspeople."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 575380.0,
      "end_time": 578360.0,
      "text": "Already, even before picking up a paintbrush,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 578600.0,
      "end_time": 582276.0,
      "text": "we had accomplished so much of the conversation and connection"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 582300.0,
      "end_time": 583540.0,
      "text": "that we had hoped for."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 584820.0,
      "end_time": 587100.0,
      "text": "And then we began to paint."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 589740.0,
      "end_time": 591876.0,
      "text": "Muslims stood by Christians"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 591900.0,
      "end_time": 595116.0,
      "text": "and atheists and agnostics and Hindus"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 595140.0,
      "end_time": 598180.0,
      "text": "and painted a mosque yellow."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 601860.0,
      "end_time": 605620.0,
      "text": "And then they all came together again and painted a church yellow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 606940.0,
      "end_time": 609360.0,
      "text": "and then another mosque,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 609600.0,
      "end_time": 610300.0,
      "text": "and then another church."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 611660.0,
      "end_time": 614260.0,
      "text": "Poets and musicians performed while we painted."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 614980.0,
      "end_time": 617116.0,
      "text": "We painted in Nairobi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 617140.0,
      "end_time": 618939.0,
      "text": "and then we painted in Mombasa."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 620660.0,
      "end_time": 624516.0,
      "text": "The local and international press did features on Colour in Faith"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 624540.0,
      "end_time": 627555.0,
      "text": "in English and French and Swahili"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 627580.0,
      "end_time": 629540.0,
      "text": "and Spanish and Somali."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 630220.0,
      "end_time": 635260.0,
      "text": "CNN highlighted Colour in Faith as a way of bringing communities together."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 637340.0,
      "end_time": 640196.0,
      "text": "And our social media platforms lit up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 640220.0,
      "end_time": 642756.0,
      "text": "connecting more and more people."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 642780.0,
      "end_time": 645860.0,
      "text": "And these neighbors continued to stay in touch."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 646660.0,
      "end_time": 650276.0,
      "text": "There are some that are pursuing politics with a platform of peace,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 650300.0,
      "end_time": 653356.0,
      "text": "and we have communities as far as Argentina and the US"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 653380.0,
      "end_time": 655636.0,
      "text": "and as close as Mali and Rwanda"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 655660.0,
      "end_time": 657476.0,
      "text": "that are asking for our help."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 657500.0,
      "end_time": 659600.0,
      "text": "And we would love to help."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 659780.0,
      "end_time": 663956.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s our dream that this project, this idea, spreads across the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 663980.0,
      "end_time": 665620.0,
      "text": "with or without our support."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 667300.0,
      "end_time": 671859.0,
      "text": "Colour in Faith is literally highlighting those who mean well in yellow."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 672820.0,
      "end_time": 675356.0,
      "text": "Colour in Faith is binding neighborhoods together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 675380.0,
      "end_time": 677876.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s our hope that when threats come knocking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 677900.0,
      "end_time": 680276.0,
      "text": "they will collectively sift fact from rumor"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 680300.0,
      "end_time": 681979.0,
      "text": "and stand in solidarity."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 683140.0,
      "end_time": 686795.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve proven that the human family can come together and send a message"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 686820.0,
      "end_time": 689196.0,
      "text": "far brighter and more powerful"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 689220.0,
      "end_time": 692600.0,
      "text": "than the voices of those that wish to do us harm."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 693140.0,
      "end_time": 694836.0,
      "text": "Though fear is infectious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 694860.0,
      "end_time": 697600.0,
      "text": "we are showing that so is hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 698660.0,
      "end_time": 699915.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 699940.0,
      "end_time": 706600.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}